		<li>
			<font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif" size="3"><span style="font-family: verdana"><span style="font-size: 12px"><span style="font-size: 10pt"><span style="font-family: arial">Ability to work as part of the team as well as independently</span></span></span></span></font></li>
